paragraphs: The famous British musician and frontman of the band Radiohead, Thom Yorke, will perform in Prague. The concert will take place on May 19th on the stage of the Fórum Karlín complex.
The musician will present his new project to Prague fans - the band The Smile, which also includes guitarist Johnny Greenwood from Radiohead.
Tickets are already on sale. You can purchase them through Ticketmaster. The cost is 1590 kroner.
